OL,5,G1100 Traffic Cops
OL,6,     FThis episode covers an alarming
OL,7,     Fsurge in burglary and car theft as
OL,8,     Fpolice units pursue a gang of
OL,9,     Fsuspected car thieves using fake
OL,10,     Fregistration plates to steal
OL,11,     Fhigh-powered vehicles.
OL,12,G1200 Traffic Cops
OL,13,     FWith reoffending rates on the rise
OL,14,     Fin the UK, we follow the Traffic
OL,15,     FCops as they are increasingly
OL,16,     Ffaced with seasoned criminals,
OL,17,     Fexperienced at evading the law.
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
