OL,5,G1800 Home and Away
OL,6,     FMackenzie blames herself. Tane
OL,7,     Fbreaks some devastating news.
OL,8,     FDavid hands Richie a learning
OL,9,     Fopportunity.
OL,10,G1830 Home and Away
OL,11,     FLacey misjudges Tane. Mackenzie
OL,12,     Fneeds space. Richie is welcomed in
OL,13,     Fby the Langhams.
OL,14,G1900 GPs Behind Closed Doors
OL,15,     FThe staff at Hall Green Health
OL,16,     FCentre are dealing with the
OL,17,     Faftermath of patient falls. Dr
OL,18,     FRazak's first patient Michael has
OL,19,     Fa nasty bruise on his arm after
OL,20,     Ffalling in his driveway.
