OL,5,G2200 A&E After Dark
OL,6,     FPolice are called to Belfast's
OL,7,     FRoyal Victoria Emergency
OL,8,     FDepartment when a female patient
OL,9,     Fbecomes very aggressive, but Dr
OL,10,     FRachel recognises she's suffering
OL,11,     Ffrom a mental health crisis.
OL,12,G2300 Skin A&E
OL,13,     FDr Toby Nelson faces the prospect
OL,14,     Fof removing a lipoma that's
OL,15,     Funderneath a patient's tattoo. Dr
OL,16,     FNatalia Spierings aims to make a
OL,17,     Fgroom-to-be picture perfect for
OL,18,     Fhis wedding photos.
