OL,5,G0000 999: Emergency Call Out
OL,6,     FA devastating car crash leads to a
OL,7,     Fmanhunt for the driver and two
OL,8,     Fpassengers. A man suffers brain
OL,9,     Fdamage after falling from a wall.
OL,10,     FA young cyclist endures a
OL,11,     Ftraumatic femur fracture.
OL,12,G0100 GPs Behind Closed Doors
OL,13,     FThe doctors and nurses at the
OL,14,     Fpractice take measures to minimise
OL,15,     Fthe over-prescription and overuse
OL,16,     Fof antibiotics in the face of a
OL,17,     Flooming crisis.
