OL,5,G0200 Casualty 24/7: Every Second Counts
OL,6,     FTwo critically ill children are
OL,7,     Frushed in by ambulance within ten
OL,8,     Fminutes of each other.
OL,9,     FTen-year-old Kai has been having
OL,10,     Fseizures, and 18-month-old Joel is
OL,11,     Fstruggling to breathe.
OL,12,G0245 Skin A&E
OL,13,     FFour top dermatologists treat
OL,14,     Fpatients for skin conditions such
OL,15,     Fas cysts, lipomas and skin tags
OL,16,     Fthat the NHS views as cosmetic but
OL,17,     Fthat can affect sufferers.
